The Pencil Code
===============

Obtaining the code: http://www.nordita.org/software/pencil-code

To get started, run one of the samples:

  unix>  cd pencil-code
  unix>  source sourceme.csh  [or . sourceme.sh]
  unix>  cd samples/conv-slab
  unix>  setup-src
  Then edit src/Makefile such that it uses the right compiler and switches
  unix>  make
  unix>  mkdir data  [I/O will be slow if you are in an NFS directory]
  unix>  start.csh
  unix>  run.csh

For more details, see the manual in the doc/ directory (also available
from the URL above).

